snippet.title: Gholazon X update + full playthrough
snippet.description:
Download link: https://forum.zdoom.org/viewtopic.php?f=43&t=68239
First few minutes focus on cool new stuff, the rest of the vid is a full playthrough of the maps included in the wad (including the secret map)
I used Nashgore while recording, it's the best gore add-on out there IMO.
Grab it here: https://forum.zdoom.org/viewtopic.php?t=62641
